column5: Simply some of the best muskie footage ever compiled all for the fun of it... closed by the BIGGEST MUSKIE EVER VIDEO TAPED IN THE WORLD. All in fun...enjoy.  58:30 is the claim of the biggest muskie on video (shes bigggg)  ** Warning** Pull up a chair chill out and relax its a great video i so enjoyed it!!!

I'll watch the show and I've seen the footage before. A bit of an overblown claim in my mind. If I won't to see fish porn this is a good show. If I want to learn how to catch more and bigger fish I much prefer the musky hunter.
I'm especially glad he didn't catch that fish if it was over 60 cause then he'd have to be the first to catch 100 over 60

I cant stand the music !(I muted and added my own)  this video shows the trials and tribulations that Muskie anglers face on any given outing...  short strikes , near misses,angler angst and depression and finally some success..  IMO it's a good compilation , thanks for posting.  Randy   ** edit= 12pk typo

Thanks for posting this video ah that last one was a Hogdoggler. looks monstrous the head alone was huge but who knows the size. this just reassures me on how much i hate seeing a single treble carefully tucked in the corner of a BIG fishes mouth.
Well...  I think we all learnt that jackpots are great lures if you don't want to land your trophies....
Haha!  Ole' Bob's gotta be the biggest tool on WFN.  Can't stand him or his show.
